/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a bustling street scene in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, giving a sense of being in the midst of the action. The sky above is a clear blue, dotted with fluffy white clouds. Buildings and shops line the street, their facades adorned with vibrant signs and advertisements in hues of red, blue, and yellow. The street itself is lined with lush green trees, providing a stark contrast to the urban landscape. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the sky, a common sight in many cityscapes. The image is bathed in the light of day, highlighting the details and colors of the scene.
